import "./App.css";
import React, { Component } from "react";
import Navbar from "./components/Navbar";
import News from "./components/News";
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from "react-router-dom";

export default class App extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Router>
          <Navbar />
          <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/">
              <News key="0" pageSize={10} country="in" category="General" />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/home">
              <News key="1" pageSize={10} country="in" category="General" />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/business">
              <News key="2" pageSize={10} country="in" category="Business" />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/entertainment">
              <News                key="3"                pageSize={10}                country="in"
                category="Entertainment"
              />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/general">
              <News key="4" pageSize={10} country="in" category="General" />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/health">
              <News key="5" pageSize={10} country="in" category="Health" />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/science">
              <News key="6" pageSize={10} country="in" category="science" />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/sports">
              <News key="7" pageSize={10} country="in" category="Sports" />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/technology">
              <News key="8" pageSize={10} country="in" category="Technology" />
            </Route>
          </Switch>
        </Router>
      </>
    );
  }
}
